sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Orch as Orchestrator<br/>8033/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+ (optional)
    participant Chunker as Chunker Service<br/>8085/TCP gRPC<br/>TLS (optional)
    participant Detector as Detector Service(s)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>TLS (optional)
    participant GenSvc as Generation Backend<br/>(TGIS/NLP/OpenAI)<br/>8033 or 8080/TCP

    Note over Client,GenSvc: Flow 1: Unary Text Generation with Detection

    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v1/task/classification-with-text-generation<br/>Auth: Passthrough headers
    Orch->>Chunker: gRPC ChunkersTokenizationTaskPredict<br/>Auth: mm-model-id header
    Chunker-->>Orch: Tokenized chunks
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents (concurrent)<br/>Auth: detector-id, x-model-name headers
    Note right of Detector: Input detection<br/>(HAP, PII, etc.)
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results
    Orch->>GenSvc: gRPC Generate / POST /v1/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer token (optional)
    GenSvc-->>Orch: Generated text
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents (concurrent)<br/>Auth: detector-id, x-model-name headers
    Note right of Detector: Output detection
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results
    Orch-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>(generation + detections)

    Note over Client,GenSvc: Flow 2: Streaming Chat Completions with Detection

    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Auth: Passthrough headers
    Orch->>Chunker: gRPC BidiStreaming<br/>Auth: mm-model-id header
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Input detection (concurrent)
    Detector-->>Orch: Input detection results
    Orch->>GenSvc: POST /v1/chat/completions (SSE stream)<br/>Auth: Bearer token
    loop Streaming chunks
        GenSvc-->>Orch: SSE chunk
        Orch->>Orch: DetectionBatcher collects chunks
        Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Batched output detection
        Detector-->>Orch: Chunk detection results
        Orch-->>Client: SSE chunk (with detections)
    end
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Whole-document detection
    Detector-->>Orch: Final detection results
    Orch-->>Client: SSE final chunk + [DONE]

    Note over Client,GenSvc: Flow 3: Content Detection Only (No Generation)

    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/text/detection/content<br/>Auth: Passthrough headers
    Orch->>Chunker: gRPC ChunkersTokenizationTaskPredict<br/>Auth: mm-model-id header
    Chunker-->>Orch: Tokenized chunks
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents (concurrent)<br/>Auth: detector-id, x-model-name headers
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results
    Orch-->>Client: JSON Response (detections only)
